### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiBase = {{baseUrl}}/api

### Get Due Flashcards - No date parameter (use current server time)
GET {{apiBase}}/study/due HTTP/1.1

### Get Due Flashcards - With specific date (past date to get all due flashcards)
GET {{apiBase}}/study/due?date=2025-12-31T23:59:59Z HTTP/1.1

### Get Due Flashcards - With specific date (current date)
GET {{apiBase}}/study/due?date=2025-11-17T10:00:00Z HTTP/1.1

### Get Due Flashcards - With specific date (future date - should return empty or fewer results)
GET {{apiBase}}/study/due?date=2025-01-01T00:00:00Z HTTP/1.1

### Get Due Flashcards - Invalid date format (should return 400)
GET {{apiBase}}/study/due?date=invalid-date HTTP/1.1

### Get Due Flashcards - Invalid date format - not ISO 8601 (should return 400)
GET {{apiBase}}/study/due?date=2025-11-17 HTTP/1.1

### Get Due Flashcards - Date without time (should return 400)
GET {{apiBase}}/study/due?date=2025-11-17T10:00:00 HTTP/1.1

### Get Due Flashcards - Valid ISO 8601 with timezone
GET {{apiBase}}/study/due?date=2025-11-17T10:00:00+01:00 HTTP/1.1

### Get Due Flashcards - Valid ISO 8601 with milliseconds
GET {{apiBase}}/study/due?date=2025-11-17T10:00:00.000Z HTTP/1.1

### Expected Response Format (200 OK)
# [
#   {
#     "id": "uuid-string",
#     "front": "Question text",
#     "back": "Answer text",
#     "interval": 2,
#     "repetition": 1,
#     "ease_factor": 2.5,
#     "due_date": "2025-11-17T00:00:00Z"
#   }
# ]

### Expected Error Response Format (400/401/500)
# {
#   "error": {
#     "code": "VALIDATION_ERROR",
#     "message": "Invalid query parameters",
#     "details": {
#       "issues": [...]
#     }
